Mondo Ride is a multinational online transportation network company founded in UAE by Troels Andersen and based in Nairobi, [Kenya]. The firm operates the Mondo ride mobile app which allows consumers with their smartphones to request for transport which is then routed to Mondo Ride drivers. The company was formed in 2015. As of 29 February 2016, the service was available in Kenya.
In 2016, the company started operations in Nairobi, Kenya.
